data.description: Welcome to this stunning home in Houston! Located just minutes away from major highways and downtown, this property offers convenience and accessibility. With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this home provides ample space for hosting guests. The modern features include granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and custom cabinets, adding a touch of elegance to the space. The high ceilings and open concept layout create a light and airy atmosphere throughout the home. Additionally, the electric gate provides security and privacy for the residents. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this beautiful property. Contact your Realtor today to schedule a private showing!
